          "$t": "Slovanka (Devuška)"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nKrásnu kresbu \"Slovanka\" pre nás vytvoril spolupracovník Peter Bros. Jedná sa o slovanskú zrubovú polozemnicu, ktorej predlohou bola rekonštrukná zrubová stavba z 9. storočia (Veľká Morava), postavená na hradisku v Bojnej. Väčšina Slovanov žila v neopevnených sídliskách. Časť &nbsp;jedného z nich vidíme práve na tomto obrázku. Ďakujeme.</div>\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgzqrfenT7t3-KGl4l8Q_NLM8l566hf1kMagimIMoLYbfVR1FA3NTnWWkV9JzzwyMHpJSlgwUE-r3bY1PlxUr9gQdFizJe2JCNhPX8unHcJcQwxHe364nDohK9k8ItnkPeMqGIb63AxgYg/s1600/SlavicWomen.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"175\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgzqrfenT7t3-KGl4l8Q_NLM8l566hf1kMagimIMoLYbfVR1FA3NTnWWkV9JzzwyMHpJSlgwUE-r3bY1PlxUr9gQdFizJe2JCNhPX8unHcJcQwxHe364nDohK9k8ItnkPeMqGIb63AxgYg/s320/SlavicWomen.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVXOS3Eq3cyw9U99PyCBQeBntQXYWxhtge8yJr01evOOEKwV46Q2HZzrZOBcaK49p2eSfBXifoMytQVsVSIhiB8_bU6jt2jiTis1EiTc3nmF4cHo0xZdqSLI7Ery7vGTLPigWqN_xkTi0/s1600/Hlavic%25CC%258Cka+web-stra%25CC%2581nky_2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"95\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhVXOS3Eq3cyw9U99PyCBQeBntQXYWxhtge8yJr01evOOEKwV46Q2HZzrZOBcaK49p2eSfBXifoMytQVsVSIhiB8_bU6jt2jiTis1EiTc3nmF4cHo0xZdqSLI7Ery7vGTLPigWqN_xkTi0/s320/Hlavic%25CC%258Cka+web-stra%25CC%2581nky_2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style